data.description: New roof installed November of 23! Lovely 3-2-2 one story on a large corner lot with a huge back yard!  Open floorplan with vaulted ceilings in family room, engineered wood flooring throughout living areas and bedrooms, tile in kitchen and baths. No carpet! The kitchen has been updated with stainless appliances, new lighting, and cabinets have been painted a fresh white! The baths have been updated with recent vanities, tile and paint.  The interior and exterior of the home has been freshly painted.  The back yard has a nice back patio area, shade trees, and the large side yard features a wood deck and a hot tub which is included! The foundation has been repaired with lifetime transferrable warranty.
